DORA Metrics
SABER Metrics in Sports

*** Dont focus on Water Melon Metrics.. Green Outside and Red Inside

Ask 5 Ws and 1 H - Why are we measuring? Who is going to use and how?
Is it really required to tie Metrics to Business.

Team = Squad
Program = Train

Qualitative Vs Quantitative Metrics
We need both. Data points are very important. 
Discount --- when given number only then it attracts people Ex: 70%. If we just say We give good discount, doesnt make sense.

