Metrics
|
Hypothesis


To tie a metric to Business, We need to start with Hypothesis, and validate them by monitoring, seeing data.

Can't change the metrics very often. When Value proposition changes, metrics may change. Some metrics may retire.

Metrics changes with Context.



Factors to consider:
------------------------------
We have diverse Stakeholders. 
There are lots of Interdependence in Org. 


Create a healthy ecosystem where metrics are dealt in transparent manner as a BAU. not a closed door topic.
Are people comfortable to report risks, failures. Only then we can have room for Innovation. - Example: Six sigma 3 defects in million. People were acared to report more defects.

